{
  "video_id": "C6mNITMY7e0",
  "title": "The hidden role informal caregivers play in health care | Scott Williams",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12952.0,
      "end_time": 16103.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s put the care back into health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16690.0,
      "end_time": 20511.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been working in the healthcare sector for the last 15 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20535.0,
      "end_time": 22912.0,
      "text": "and one of the things that drew me to this sector"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22936.0,
      "end_time": 27154.0,
      "text": "was my interest in the care component of our healthcare systems --"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27178.0,
      "end_time": 28517.0,
      "text": "more specifically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28541.0,
      "end_time": 31154.0,
      "text": "to the invaluable role played by carers."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32173.0,
      "end_time": 35838.0,
      "text": "Now, how many of you in this room consider yourself a carer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38473.0,
      "end_time": 41720.0,
      "text": "By this, I mean how many of you have cared for someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41960.0,
      "end_time": 44723.0,
      "text": "suffering from an illness, injury or disability?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44747.0,
      "end_time": 46873.0,
      "text": "Can you raise your hand if this is the case?"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49119.0,
      "end_time": 50531.0,
      "text": "About half of the room."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51316.0,
      "end_time": 53626.0,
      "text": "I want to thank all of you who raised your hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53650.0,
      "end_time": 55814.0,
      "text": "for the time that you&#39;ve spent as a carer."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55838.0,
      "end_time": 58480.0,
      "text": "What you do is extremely precious."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59813.0,
      "end_time": 62204.0,
      "text": "I am a former cared-for patient myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62868.0,
      "end_time": 65961.0,
      "text": "When I was a teenager, I suffered from Lyme disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65985.0,
      "end_time": 69660.0,
      "text": "and underwent 18 months of antibiotic treatment."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70250.0,
      "end_time": 72480.0,
      "text": "I was repeatedly misdiagnosed:"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72521.0,
      "end_time": 76964.0,
      "text": "bacterial meningitis, fibromyalgia, you name it."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76988.0,
      "end_time": 78554.0,
      "text": "They couldn&#39;t figure it out."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79141.0,
      "end_time": 82606.0,
      "text": "And if I&#39;m standing here in front of you today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82630.0,
      "end_time": 84259.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s because I owe my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 84283.0,
      "end_time": 87200.0,
      "text": "to the stubbornness and commitment of one carer."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88187.0,
      "end_time": 90155.0,
      "text": "He did everything he could for me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90179.0,
      "end_time": 93651.0,
      "text": "driving long distances from one treatment center to another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93675.0,
      "end_time": 95548.0,
      "text": "searching for the best option,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96276.0,
      "end_time": 99800.0,
      "text": "and above all, never giving up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99320.0,
      "end_time": 101150.0,
      "text": "despite the difficulties he encountered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101400.0,
      "end_time": 104208.0,
      "text": "including from a work and quality-of-life perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 104867.0,
      "end_time": 106605.0,
      "text": "That was my father."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106629.0,
      "end_time": 110798.0,
      "text": "I recovered, and this is largely thanks to his dedication."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 111631.0,
      "end_time": 114811.0,
      "text": "This experience turned me into a patient advocate."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115478.0,
      "end_time": 120259.0,
      "text": "The closer I looked, the more I saw carers providing the same kind of support"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120284.0,
      "end_time": 122594.0,
      "text": "that my father provided to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122618.0,
      "end_time": 125993.0,
      "text": "and playing a crucial role in the healthcare system."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126686.0,
      "end_time": 129307.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think it&#39;s an exaggeration to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129330.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131810.0,
      "text": "that without informal carers like him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131835.0,
      "end_time": 134270.0,
      "text": "our health and social systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 134510.0,
      "end_time": 135373.0,
      "text": "would crumble."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136148.0,
      "end_time": 139514.0,
      "text": "And yet, they&#39;re largely going unrecognized."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 140828.0,
      "end_time": 143926.0,
      "text": "I am now a long-distance carer for my mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 144687.0,
      "end_time": 146972.0,
      "text": "who suffers from multiple chronic conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 148400.0,
      "end_time": 151786.0,
      "text": "I understand, now more than ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 151811.0,
      "end_time": 153886.0,
      "text": "the demands that caregivers face."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154942.0,
      "end_time": 157126.0,
      "text": "With aging populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 157150.0,
      "end_time": 158975.0,
      "text": "economic instability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158999.0,
      "end_time": 160971.0,
      "text": "healthcare system stress"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160995.0,
      "end_time": 163932.0,
      "text": "and increased incidents of long-term chronic care needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 164690.0,
      "end_time": 167408.0,
      "text": "the importance and demands on family caregivers"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 167432.0,
      "end_time": 168763.0,
      "text": "are greater than ever."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 169886.0,
      "end_time": 173777.0,
      "text": "Carers all over the world are sacrificing their own physical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 173801.0,
      "end_time": 176587.0,
      "text": "financial and psychosocial well-being"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 176611.0,
      "end_time": 178442.0,
      "text": "to provide care for their loved ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179556.0,
      "end_time": 181956.0,
      "text": "Carers have their own limits and needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 181980.0,
      "end_time": 184374.0,
      "text": "and in absence of adequate support,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 184398.0,
      "end_time": 186752.0,
      "text": "many could be stretched to the breaking point."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 187858.0,
      "end_time": 191451.0,
      "text": "Once seen as a personal and private matter in family life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192132.0,
      "end_time": 195643.0,
      "text": "unpaid caregiving has formed the invisible backbone"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195667.0,
      "end_time": 198988.0,
      "text": "of our health and social systems all over the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200469.0,
      "end_time": 202863.0,
      "text": "Many of these carers are even in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202887.0,
      "end_time": 204203.0,
      "text": "as we have just seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 205310.0,
      "end_time": 207639.0,
      "text": "Who are they, and how many are they?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208217.0,
      "end_time": 210583.0,
      "text": "What are the challenges that they are facing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 210607.0,
      "end_time": 214406.0,
      "text": "And, above all, how can we make sure that their value to patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 214430.0,
      "end_time": 216748.0,
      "text": "our healthcare system and society"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216772.0,
      "end_time": 217929.0,
      "text": "is recognized?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 219670.0,
      "end_time": 221648.0,
      "text": "Anyone can be a carer, really:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 222357.0,
      "end_time": 226233.0,
      "text": "a 15-year-old girl caring for a parent with multiple sclerosis;"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 227740.0,
      "end_time": 229978.0,
      "text": "a 40-year-old man juggling full-time work"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 230200.0,
      "end_time": 232945.0,
      "text": "while caring for his family who lives far away;"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 233623.0,
      "end_time": 237310.0,
      "text": "a 60-year-old man caring for his wife who has terminal cancer;"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 238279.0,
      "end_time": 241414.0,
      "text": "or an 80-year-old woman caring for her husband"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 241438.0,
      "end_time": 243730.0,
      "text": "who has Alzheimer&#39;s disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 243997.0,
      "end_time": 247889.0,
      "text": "The things carers do for their patients are varied."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 247913.0,
      "end_time": 249609.0,
      "text": "They provide personal care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 249633.0,
      "end_time": 251641.0,
      "text": "like getting someone dressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 251665.0,
      "end_time": 253209.0,
      "text": "feeding them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 253234.0,
      "end_time": 254661.0,
      "text": "helping them to the bathroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 256678.0,
      "text": "helping them move about."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 257356.0,
      "end_time": 260966.0,
      "text": "They also provide a significant level of medical care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 260991.0,
      "end_time": 265938.0,
      "text": "because they often know a lot about their loved one&#39;s condition and needs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 265962.0,
      "end_time": 268851.0,
      "text": "sometimes better than the patients themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268875.0,
      "end_time": 272453.0,
      "text": "who may be paralyzed or confused by their diagnosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 273284.0,
      "end_time": 274834.0,
      "text": "In those situations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 275350.0,
      "end_time": 279310.0,
      "text": "carers are also advocates for the patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 280769.0,
      "end_time": 282966.0,
      "text": "Also of critical importance"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 283631.0,
      "end_time": 287734.0,
      "text": "is the fact that carers also provide emotional support."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 288338.0,
      "end_time": 290313.0,
      "text": "They organize doctor&#39;s appointments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 291107.0,
      "end_time": 292831.0,
      "text": "they manage finances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 292855.0,
      "end_time": 296108.0,
      "text": "and they also deal with daily household tasks."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 297180.0,
      "end_time": 299833.0,
      "text": "These challenges are challenges that we can&#39;t ignore."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 300633.0,
      "end_time": 304790.0,
      "text": "There are currently more than 100 million carers"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 304103.0,
      "end_time": 307866.0,
      "text": "providing 80 percent of care across Europe."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308617.0,
      "end_time": 310930.0,
      "text": "And even if these numbers are impressive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 310954.0,
      "end_time": 315388.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re most likely underestimated, given the lack of recognition of carers."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 315412.0,
      "end_time": 316705.0,
      "text": "As we have just seen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 316730.0,
      "end_time": 320119.0,
      "text": "many of you in this room weren&#39;t sure if you could be qualified"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 320143.0,
      "end_time": 322222.0,
      "text": "or considered to be a carer."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 322246.0,
      "end_time": 324858.0,
      "text": "Many of you probably thought I was referring to a nurse"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 324882.0,
      "end_time": 326803.0,
      "text": "or some other healthcare professional."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 327602.0,
      "end_time": 329960.0,
      "text": "Also stunning"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 329120.0,
      "end_time": 332838.0,
      "text": "are the benefits that carers bring to our societies."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 332862.0,
      "end_time": 336774.0,
      "text": "I want to give you just one example from Australia in 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 337607.0,
      "end_time": 340960.0,
      "text": "The annual value provided by informal carers"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 340984.0,
      "end_time": 343120.0,
      "text": "to those suffering from mental illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 343360.0,
      "end_time": 347953.0,
      "text": "was evaluated at 13.2 billion Australian dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 348431.0,
      "end_time": 351974.0,
      "text": "This is nearly two times what the Australian government spends"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 351998.0,
      "end_time": 353957.0,
      "text": "on mental health services annually."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 353982.0,
      "end_time": 356210.0,
      "text": "These numbers, among others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 356234.0,
      "end_time": 359393.0,
      "text": "demonstrate that if carers were to stop caring tomorrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 359417.0,
      "end_time": 362714.0,
      "text": "our health and social systems would crumble."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 364168.0,
      "end_time": 366931.0,
      "text": "And while the importance of these millions of silent carers"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 366955.0,
      "end_time": 368300.0,
      "text": "cannot be denied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 368890.0,
      "end_time": 370938.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve largely been unnoticed"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 370962.0,
      "end_time": 373918.0,
      "text": "by governments, healthcare systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 373942.0,
      "end_time": 375381.0,
      "text": "and private entities."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 377420.0,
      "end_time": 381277.0,
      "text": "In addition, carers are facing enormous personal challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 381792.0,
      "end_time": 385791.0,
      "text": "Many carers face higher costs and can face financial difficulties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 385815.0,
      "end_time": 388901.0,
      "text": "given the fact that they may not be able to work full time"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 388925.0,
      "end_time": 391617.0,
      "text": "or they may not be able to hold down a job altogether."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 392330.0,
      "end_time": 393530.0,
      "text": "Many studies have shown"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 393554.0,
      "end_time": 396553.0,
      "text": "that often carers sacrifice their own health and well-being"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 396577.0,
      "end_time": 398580.0,
      "text": "in order to care for their loved ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 399395.0,
      "end_time": 403490.0,
      "text": "Many carers spend so much time caring for their loved ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 403740.0,
      "end_time": 406124.0,
      "text": "that often their family and their relationships can suffer."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 406941.0,
      "end_time": 408628.0,
      "text": "Many carers report that often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 408653.0,
      "end_time": 411355.0,
      "text": "their employers don&#39;t have adequate policies in place"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 411379.0,
      "end_time": 412659.0,
      "text": "to support them."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 413157.0,
      "end_time": 414849.0,
      "text": "There has been improvement, though,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 414874.0,
      "end_time": 417180.0,
      "text": "in the recognition of carers around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 417718.0,
      "end_time": 420262.0,
      "text": "Just a few years ago, an umbrella organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 420286.0,
      "end_time": 424608.0,
      "text": "called the International Alliance of Carer Organizations, or IACO,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 424632.0,
      "end_time": 428498.0,
      "text": "was formed to bring together carer groups from all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 428522.0,
      "end_time": 430631.0,
      "text": "to provide strategic direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 430655.0,
      "end_time": 432676.0,
      "text": "facilitate information sharing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 432701.0,
      "end_time": 436271.0,
      "text": "as well as actively advocate for carers on an international level."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 437360.0,
      "end_time": 441350.0,
      "text": "Private entities are also starting to recognize the situation of carers."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 441836.0,
      "end_time": 444101.0,
      "text": "I am proud that my personal engagement"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 444125.0,
      "end_time": 446754.0,
      "text": "and enthusiasm towards this topic of carers"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 446778.0,
      "end_time": 448866.0,
      "text": "found an echo in my own workplace."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 449612.0,
      "end_time": 452106.0,
      "text": "My company is committed to this cause"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 452130.0,
      "end_time": 454884.0,
      "text": "and has developed an unprecedented framework"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 454908.0,
      "end_time": 457787.0,
      "text": "for its employees and society as a whole."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 458471.0,
      "end_time": 460900.0,
      "text": "The objective is to empower carers"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 460924.0,
      "end_time": 463890.0,
      "text": "to improve their own health and well-being"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 463113.0,
      "end_time": 465699.0,
      "text": "and bring about a greater balance to their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 466875.0,
      "end_time": 470180.0,
      "text": "Nevertheless, much more needs to be done"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 470204.0,
      "end_time": 473980.0,
      "text": "to complement these relatively isolated initiatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 474500.0,
      "end_time": 476914.0,
      "text": "Our societies are facing increased health pressures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 476938.0,
      "end_time": 479223.0,
      "text": "including aging populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 479247.0,
      "end_time": 482654.0,
      "text": "increased incidence of cancer and chronic conditions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 482678.0,
      "end_time": 484713.0,
      "text": "widespread inequality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 484737.0,
      "end_time": 486201.0,
      "text": "amongst many others."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 486862.0,
      "end_time": 488726.0,
      "text": "To confront these challenges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 488750.0,
      "end_time": 492409.0,
      "text": "policymakers must look beyond traditional healthcare pathways"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 492433.0,
      "end_time": 493781.0,
      "text": "and employment policies"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 494418.0,
      "end_time": 496771.0,
      "text": "and recognize that informal care"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 496795.0,
      "end_time": 499861.0,
      "text": "will continue to form the bedrock of care."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 501456.0,
      "end_time": 503763.0,
      "text": "Caring for someone should be a choice"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 504644.0,
      "end_time": 508757.0,
      "text": "and should be done without putting one&#39;s own well-being in the balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511129.0,
      "end_time": 514962.0,
      "text": "But to really put the care back into health care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 515671.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521115.00000000006,
      "text": "what&#39;s needed is a deep, societal, structural change."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 522130.0,
      "end_time": 524675.0,
      "text": "And this can only happen through a change in mindset."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 525371.0,
      "end_time": 527194.0,
      "text": "And this can start today."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 528182.0,
      "end_time": 531660.0,
      "text": "Today, we can plant the seed for a change"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 531900.0,
      "end_time": 533210.0,
      "text": "for millions of carers around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 533927.0,
      "end_time": 535500.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s what I want to suggest:"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 536216.0,
      "end_time": 537616.0,
      "text": "when you go home today"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 538318.0,
      "end_time": 540641.0,
      "text": "or to the office tomorrow morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 540666.0,
      "end_time": 541959.0,
      "text": "embrace a carer."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 543120.0,
      "end_time": 544215.0,
      "text": "Thank them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 544756.0,
      "end_time": 546588.0,
      "text": "offer him or her a bit of help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 547284.0,
      "end_time": 551242.0,
      "text": "maybe even volunteer as a carer yourself for a couple hours a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 552260.0,
      "end_time": 554911.0,
      "text": "If carers around the world felt better recognized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 554935.0,
      "end_time": 557743.0,
      "text": "it would not only improve their own health and well-being"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 557768.0,
      "end_time": 559476.0,
      "text": "and sense of fulfillment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 559500.0,
      "end_time": 562890.0,
      "text": "but it would also improve the lives of those that they&#39;re caring for."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 563531.0,
      "end_time": 565000.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s care more."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 565484.0,
      "end_time": 566635.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 566659.0,
      "end_time": 569682.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}